description: CENTRALLY-LOCATED PENTHOUSE CONDO WITH TWO PRIVATE DECKS   Open-concept kitchen features stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinet space and a granite breakfast bar that leads into the living area. Primary bedroom fits a king-sized bed and showcases large windows, walk-in closet and en-suite bath. Second bedroom fits a queen and is situated just across the hall from second full bath with sleek stone shower. In-unit laundry, air conditioning, high ceilings and hardwood floors throughout. Sliders off the living area offer access to large 163 sq ft private deck that's just perfect for entertaining. Spiral staircase leads to second 100 sq ft private roof deck where you can catch some sun and a cool breeze. Pet friendly. Deeded storage in basement. Location is excellent near American Provisions, The Playwright and Stats Bar & Grill. Easy access to Seaport and M St beach. Don't miss out on the chance to see this lovely, most affordable 2 bed/2 bath condo in all of South Boston!
